data.description: This 3 bed 2 bath home is in the process of being completely updated.  New roof in April of 2021 warranty will transfer to new owner, foundation repair in April of 2021 with available transferable lifetime warranty. Entire house is getting a fresh coat of paint inside and out in May of 2021. Large covered back porch on south side will help keep the summer sun off. Beautiful vinyl plank floors in process of being installed throughout the home, kitchen is getting new cabinets, granite counter tops, sink, range, dishwasher and microwave.  Bathrooms getting a facelift too with fresh tile in shower tub areas, and new toilets and sinks.  This home will be move in ready and will make someone happy for years to come.
